&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An enthusiastic and highly motivated nurse is required to join the existing team who help shape the future of critical care within this Trust. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Our 12 bedded mixed Intensive Care Unit/High Dependency Unit has a commitment to high standards of care and continued learning and can offer the successful candidate a new challenge with tremendous job satisfaction in a friendly and well supported environment. There is an excellent induction package and training in a modern and upgraded intensive care/high dependency unit supported by a clinical information management system. The unit also operates a 12 hour shift system. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ICU/HDU experience is desirable. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Permanent Full time and Part time hours available&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
